                        "created_at": "1767684422",
                        "id": "18006798776832090",
                        "text": "Part 1 of Must-Buy Items in Japan \ud83c\uddef\ud83c\uddf5\ud83d\udc95\n\u2028Save this for your next Japan trip!\nShopping in Japan can feel overwhelming but in the best way possible. It\u2019s truly a paradise for snacks and beauty finds, and with limited luggage space, choosing what to buy isn\u2019t easy \ud83e\udd72\nIn this video, I\u2019m sharing my top must-buy recommendations from Japan that are totally worth it.\n\nPro tips:\u2028\u2022 Check out Don Quijote, but don\u2019t skip gems like Daiso or Seria\u2028\u2022 Always carry your passport for tax-free shopping\u2028\u2022 Leave extra space in your luggage (or pack an extra bag for shopping)\u2028\u2022 Pick up convenience store merch like 7-Eleven socks and Lawson tote bags\u2028\u2022 You can\u2019t go wrong with Canmake beauty products as they are amazing across all categories \n\n#japan #traveljapan #japanshopping #travel #tokyo"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
